ProductName: Mott's 100% Original Apple Juice - 6pk/8 fl oz Bottles
Description: Nothing satisfies quite like Mott’s Original Apple Juice. Packed with ripe apple flavor, Mott’s Original Apple Juice is 100% fruit juice and delivers 2 servings of fruit in each 8 fl. oz cup, per current USDA Dietary Guidelines. Mott’s Original Apple Juice is the perfect refreshment at dinnertime, lunchtime, or any time. Apples have always nourished us, inspired us, and provided for us. Treat your family to the classic taste of Mott’s Original Apple Juice.
